Compile             : $make
Compile and Install : $make install
Cleaning            : $make clean

Arguments >

    0 -> executable file
    1 -> initial range
    2 -> jump range
    3 -> num jumps
    4 -> initial power
    5 -> power reduction
    6 -> input file


Example Run >

    ./[executable file] [initial range] [jump range] [num jumps] [initial power] [power reduction] [input file]


Example Input File Values >

    0 0 100 100 Lokman_Hekim
    2 0 100 500 Kara_Murat
    3 0 400 450 Koca_Yusuf
    4 0 45 400 Nasrettin_Hoca
    4 1 300 600 Cengiz_Han

Example Run and Output > 

    Command ->
        ./main 5 1 2 500 0.25 small.txt

    Output ->
        Kara_Murat 400
        Koca_Yusuf 50
        Nasrettin_Hoca 355
        Koca_Yusuf 50
        Nasrettin_Hoca 355
        Cengiz_Han 300
        Toplam_İyileşme: 655
